dict.string: This beautiful sticker pack, created by Tabbykittyco, combines sticky notes, frames, and polaroids, in beautiful neutral colors. Perfect for digital planners, vision and mood boards, notebooks, and scrapbooking. Enjoy the feel of organic paper texture by adding these ripped paper effects to your notes!
Make your plans more fun with these cheerful, colorful stickers! Created with love by Tabbykittyco, this is a collection of hand-drawn doodles, Designed to stand out on dark-mode digital planners.

Express your thoughts more clearly with icons! Designed by Tabbykittyco, these icons are perfect for comprehending your plans at a glance. This versatile set is well-suited for dark and light mode notes.

Hand-drawn by Tabbykittyco, this sticker pack consists of plant and flower doodles. You can fill these cute stickers with color to make them yours truly. (We recommend using the highlighter to add color)

Say it with a sticker! Handcrafted by our Noteshelf team, these exquisite pastel stickers will add a splash of color to your notes. Designed to pair perfectly with the colorful planner, you can add these stickers to any of your notes.

Spread the joy and celebrate the most wonderful time of the year with these delightful Christmas-themed stickers created by DGPDesignsCo. These stickers are perfect for your gift ideas, holiday to-do list, or simply to add some festive spirit to your notes.
